{"tid":378736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經典電影種族歧視？美劇院拒播《亂世佳人》","createTime":"2017-08-28T17:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T02:03:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05dbaf479edd350f204ef3675052259987640e88","tid":378736,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170827/photo/bknint-20170827180212024-0827_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170827185100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170827%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170827180212024-0827_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170827185100&h=845e81b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於《亂世佳人》中飾演美國南方女黑奴的麥克丹尼爾，在1940年成為首位奪得奧斯卡金像獎的非裔人。她當時哽咽着說：「希望我可以成為我的種族，以至電影界的榮耀。」不過在77年之後、左右翼對立加劇的今天，南方黑人為主社區孟菲斯卻指摘電影內容種族歧視，老牌的奧芬劇院表示為了順應民意，結束一年一度重映該電影的傳統，引起各派民眾激烈爭論。<br />\n<br />\n奧芬劇院集團主席巴特森上周五（25日）發表聲明指：「我們在8月11日重映《亂世佳人》時，接到大量意見。我們決定，作為以娛樂、教育及啟蒙大眾為已任的組織，我們不可以放映一齣被大部分當地社區人士視為欠缺敏感度（insensitive）的電影。」<br />\n<br />\n孟菲斯奧芬劇院每年8月均會放映一連串經典電影，其中《亂世佳人》已連續34年重映，更試過一年放映4次。巴特森強調，維珍尼亞州發生車撞左翼示威人士之前，劇院已決定今年不會放映。他表示：「每年都會有人對電影內容提出質疑，但今年社交網上風暴般的爭論也衝擊到我們的社區。」位於田納西州的孟菲斯，人口中有64%為黑人。<br />\n<br />\n在《亂世佳人》電影中，除了女主角郝思嘉在南北戰爭中的成長與苦戀，觀眾亦對忠心的黑奴保姆「媽咪（Mammy）」印象深刻。麥克丹尼爾憑此角色奪得奧斯卡女配角獎，當時只准白人進入的酒店，破例准許麥克丹尼爾進入參加頒獎禮，不過她要與白人經理人同坐一張二人桌。榮譽背後，媽咪等黑人角色同時是數十年來種族爭議的話題之一，被指描繪不夠深刻、歡樂簡單得尤如漫畫角色，電影被批評淡化奴隸制對黑人的殘害。<br />\n<br />\n大批網民到奧芬劇院的社交網頁面留言表示不滿，有人稱：「任何一件事都會得罪少數族裔，令人感到厭倦。歷史就是歷史！」有人認為《亂世佳人》就是打破黑白之間藩籬的起點，另有人大罵自由派才是製造歧視的黑手。但有孟菲斯居民留言反駁：「我們會慢慢在社區中消滅一切白人至上主義的宣傳。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170827/bknint-20170827180212024-0827_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170827%2Fbknint-20170827180212024-0827_17011_001.html&d=TGuA74kbfzTUufBc9i%2FkiAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=8128f7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170827/bknint-20170827180212024-0827_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ce85cb904271eaaf1b631b26dcf1bad235f2f9da","tid":378736,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21077642_1952924094965155_982300200676623222_n.jpg?oh=6ec17903e8c046829efa7f5683af6e3f&amp;oe=5A2097AB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21077642_1952924094965155_982300200676623222_n.jpg%3Foh%3D6ec17903e8c046829efa7f5683af6e3f%26oe%3D5A2097AB&h=73233072&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b2a10e60da7ed01cec267bf8f62323704ca9b24","tid":378736,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"殺曬所有黑人咪再冇歧視"},{"pid":"8b31105b1d48e57b8b1bc818203ed8542c05e0ef","tid":378736,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881a8925b27841fc263035747117e813a161302b","tid":378736,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"黑人團體同女權份子一樣咁討厭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8267225a96ab2f0818d84123aaa38c2234db6a6f","tid":378736,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:04:51.000Z","msg":"屌你個老母真係好撚煩 在美國福利著數拿盡 仲想點"},{"pid":"aea96a63dd2b58f6f3c7a5912df3ae1239ae6856","tid":378736,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d2b8cc48d4c294bed46ccf3e871a3db8bab35b","tid":378736,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:44:33.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，咁都叫歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cae20d529e7e8b6f54ba9c750424830b9a83ecf","tid":378736,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:38:56.000Z","msg":"轉頭歧視黃種人"},{"pid":"45f11d5b3e800548acfe8b5cee2143bd99473add","tid":378736,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"文革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246c5b9bf53142383adfe45437f15d42d7e2e0d1","tid":378736,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"好快連魔戒都標籤做白人至上電影"},{"pid":"43e4fd02aba8076b283877b58277dabf1fa0fa87","tid":378736,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:55:56.000Z","msg":"文化大革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a46a8b4125d6f07811afa1e270ad83020b47856","tid":378736,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉頭歧視黃種人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一邊歧視亞洲人，一邊屌白鬼歧視<br />\n個個都係為自己"}]}